title: 204: 10 Takeaways from Week 1
itunes:title: 204: 10 Takeaways from Week 1
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks premiere their first Sunday night podcast reacting to the ten biggest storylines from this weekend's action. The guys highlight what they thought of DeShone Kizer and Deshaun Watson's debuts, the impressive performance from the Ravens defense, and much more.
